This paper is about designing a new approach to enable robots to perceive human group motion in real time to anticipate future actions and synthesize their own motion accordingly. The paper focuses on joint action, in which humans and robots move together synchronously. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is Robotics (cs.RO), followed by Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV).
